| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4369 — Recovery Inhibition (bianlian)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 898572e2-8d3d-5795-a3a0-c1b7c40da57e"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
